05:36.169 --> 05:37.504
Tilly:
Vroom! Whoo‐hoo!

05:37.587 --> 05:39.506
Oh, yeah.

05:39.589 --> 05:40.757
Tilly, wait!

05:40.841 --> 05:41.716
Tilly: Vroom!

05:41.800 --> 05:43.301
Beep, beep! ( giggles )

05:43.385 --> 05:46.721
